data.title: "Verbotene Liebe" Episode #1.3709 (TV Episode 2010)
data.meta_description: Episode #1.3709: Directed by Kerstin Krause. With Wolfram Grandezka, Miriam Lahnstein, Jasmin Gassmann, Milan Marcus. Ansgar in jail and the others von Lahnsteins in the castle are baffled by Lydia's public homicide confession. It makes the scandal even more spectacular, hence damning for the budding wood firm. Sebastian suffers unbearably now he realizes his wife is an utter adulteress and throws her out. Constantine rather uneasily celebrates Nathalie's dream teaching job with her husband, who still doesn't suspect her infidelity with the ideal Spanish pupil.
